criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  American Society of Anesthesiologists physical status Ⅰ-Ⅱ ;

          -  Weight 50-75 kg;

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Long history of alcohol or analgesic drugs(including opioid ) abuse;

          -  Heavy smoking;

          -  Motion sickness;

          -  Long history of PONV;

          -  Chronic pain;

          -  Complicated with severe heart、brain or kidney disease.
